summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending page 17 of the Official Land Use Map, (Vol. 22 of Plats, page 73, of the Records of King County) to rezone property located at 11550 26th Avenue NE from Single Family 7200 (SF 7200) to Commercial 1 with a 30' height limit and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Pierre Properties, LLC, C.F. 304023 Application. 2001586)
